                                        <h5 class="main-heading">Selecting a Journal</h5>
                                        <p>While selecting a journal, there are a few things that you must check to ensure journal suitability and minimize the chances of outright rejection. Some of these are as follows:</p>
                                        <ul class="default-list b-points">
                                            <li> Scope of study</li>
                                            <li> Target journal type (scope, focus, etc.)</li>
                                            <li> Urgency to publish</li>
                                            <li> Accessibility features (open access, print only, etc.)</li>
                                            <li>Type of article</li>
                                            <li>Significance of article in its field of specialty</li>
                                        </ul>
                                   
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
