                                        </div>
                                        <p>Years of experience as a published author can help you evaluate these parameters with ease. At Enago Publication Support, you can get access to Journal Selection experts in your area of research. Simply send us your criteria, and we will present you with the 3 to 5 journals best suited to your manuscript and preferences through our Journal Selection service.
</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tab-detail-btn text-center w-100 mt-3">
